        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <date>Decmb 21<hi rend="sup">st</hi> /55</date>
            </p>
            <p>Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Having seen your reply to <persName>Dr Raphall's</persName>
                wherein<lb/> you promise favorably to notice my Heb. Grammar in your valuable
                Pe-<lb/>riodical I trust you will do so in the next Number, as think an extract
                from<lb/> it put into the circular I am advised to send about will do much towards
                procuring<lb/> subscribers to the work. I intend publishing it at 5<add>?</add>
                though in <placeName>England</placeName> no less<lb/> than 3000 copies were disposed
                of at double that sum. I regret very much<lb/> that I am unable to supply you with a
                copy to enable you to judge for yourself<lb/> of its superiority to any other, as it
                is deemed by all who are competent to judge<lb/> of it. The whole of the last
                edition published in <placeName>London</placeName> 6 months ago I have<lb/> sold
                previous to my leaving there, with the exception of 6 copies which<lb/> were soon
                snatched away at my arrival here and consequently I am now in<lb/> want of one, in
                my professional pursuit as a teacher I shall be happy to present<lb/> you with one
                of my next Edition    Remaining    Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Your's very respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <persName role="author">S. Newman</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>New York 144 Amos St. Hudson St.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>The <addressee>Revd Mr Leeser</addressee></p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>The <addressee>Revd Mr Leeser</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Editor of the Occident</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
